  "body": "<div id=\"post-view221235358225\" class=\" pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea221235358225\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153\" class=\"se_doc_viewer se_body_wrap se_theme_transparent \" data-docversion=\"\">\n<div class=\"se_doc_header_start\" id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_se_doc_header_start\"></div>\n<!-- SE_DOC_HEADER_START -->\n<div id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_viewer_head\" class=\"se_viewer_head\"></div>\n<div class=\"se_component_wrap\">\n<div class=\"se_component se_documentTitle documentTitle_blog  is-fill\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea is-fill se_align-left\">\n        <!-- --> \n<div class=\"blog2_series\">\n\t<a href=\"/PostList.naver?blogId=isuhani&categoryNo=15&from=postList\" class=\"pcol2\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.category','');\">비염</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pcol1\"> \n<!--\n -->\n        <!-- SE_DOC_HEADER_TITLE_TOP-->\n     \t<div id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_se_doc_title_top\" class=\"se_doc_title_top\"></div>\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n        \t<div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_D2\">\n\t            <div class=\"se_editView se_title\">\n\t                <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <h3 class=\"se_textarea\">\n                            <!-- -->중이염치료 [남성역 소아한의원]<!-- -->\n                            \n                        </h3>\n                        \n                        \n\t                </div>\n\t            </div>\n\t        </div>\n        </div><!-- SE_DOC_HEADER_TITLE_MIDDLE-->\n        <div id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_se_doc_title_middle\" class=\"se_doc_title_middle\"></div>\n        <!-- SE_DOC_HEADER_CONTENTS_START -->\n        <!-- -->\n</div>\n<div class=\"blog2_container\">\n    <span class=\"writer\">\n        <span class=\"area_profile\"><a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani\" class=\"link\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.profile', '');\" target=\"_top\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9967affe77f2e25b.jpg\" class=\"img\" alt=\"프로파일\"></a></span>\n        <span class=\"nick\"><a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani\" class=\"link pcol2\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.username', '');\" target=\"_top\">문학진 나효석 원장</a></span>\n        <span class=\"desc\">\n            <i class=\"dot\"> ・ </i>\n            <span class=\"se_publishDate pcol2\">2018. 3. 23. 9:58</span>\n        </span>\n    </span>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"blog2_post_function\">\n\t<a href=\"#\" id=\"copyBtn_221235358225\" class=\"url pcol2 _setClipboard _returnFalse _se3copybtn _transPosition\" title=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/221235358225\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\" >URL 복사</a>\n\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn_buddy btn_addbuddy pcol2 _buddy_popup_btn _returnFalse _rosRestrictAll\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.addnei', '');\"><i class=\"ico\"></i> 이웃추가<i class=\"aline\"></i></a>\n\t<div class=\"overflow_menu\" >\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn_overflow_menu _open_overflowmenu pcol2 _param(221235358225) _returnFalse\" role=\"button\" area-haspopup=\"true\" area-expanded=\"false\"><span class=\"blind\">본문 기타 기능</span></a>\n\t\t<div id=\"overflowmenu-221235358225\" class=\"lyr_overflow_menu _overflowmenu_layer\" area-hidden=\"true\">\n               <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"window.nsc='blog.post';return false;\" id=\"_title_spiButton\" class=\"naver-splugin btn_splugin share _title_share\"\n                  data-style=\"unity\"\n                  data-url=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/221235358225\"\n                  data-oninitialize=\"splugin_oninitialize(1);\"\n                  data-me-display=\"off\"\n                  data-likeServiceId=\"BLOG\"\n                  data-likeContentsId=\"isuhani_221235358225\"\n                  data-spic-cid=\"221235358225\"\n                  data-logDomain=\"https://proxy.blog.naver.com/spi/v1/api/shareLog\"\n                  data-canonical-url=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/221235358225\"\n                  data-option=\"{baseElement:'_title_spiButton', layerPosition:'outside-bottom', align:'right', marginLeft:0, marginTop:4}\">\n                   공유하기\n                <span class=\"ico_share _title_share_icon\"></span>\n               </a>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"_report _param(https://srp2.naver.com/report?svc=BLG&exit=close&ctype=AA01&cwriterenc=bMqVKkvHx%2FV8PjrUUdb4qKPZ9PrCTQMoKf61zshMnIY%3D&ctitle=%EC%A4%91%EC%9D%B4%EC%97%BC%EC%B9%98%EB%A3%8C%20%5B%EB%82%A8%EC%84%B1%EC%97%AD%20%EC%86%8C%EC%95%84%ED%95%9C%EC%9D%98%EC%9B%90%5D&cwriter=isuh***&dark=disable&memtype=Y&env=pc&cnickname=isuh***&vsvc=BLG&cid=isuhani%40%4049462061%40%40mylog%40%40221235358225) _returnFalse\">신고하기<span class=\"ico_report\"></span></a>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n    <input type=\"text\" value=\"https://blog.naver.com/isuhani/221235358225\" alt=\"url\" class=\"copyTargetUrl\" style=\"display:none;\" title=\"URL 복사\">\n</div>\n<!--\n -->\n        <!-- SE_DOC_HEADER_CONTENTS_END -->\n        <!-- SE_DOC_HEADER_TITLE_BOTTOM-->\n        <div id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_se_doc_title_bottom\" class=\"se_doc_title_bottom\"></div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<!-- B2C 상품 -->\n<!-- _BLOG_CONTENTS_HEADER_TAIL -->\n<!-- SE_DOC_HEADER_END -->\n<div class=\"se_doc_header_end\" id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_se_doc_header_end\"></div>\n<div class=\"se_doc_contents_start\" id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_se_doc_contents_start\"></div>\n<!-- SE_DOC_CONTENTS_START -->\n<div class=\"se_component_wrap sect_dsc __se_component_area\">\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><br><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span> 중이염은 감기와 동반해서, 혹은 감기 후에 합병증으로 흔히 발생합니다.<br></span><span>애들이 항생제를 복용하게 되는 주요 질환 중 하나죠. <br></span><span></span><br><span>중이염의 원인은 다양한데, 주로 목과 코의 질환(감기, 비염, 부비동염, 축농증 등)이 원인이 되는 경우가 많습니다. </span><span><br></span><span></span><br><span>&nbsp;고막보다 더 깊이 있는 '중이 - 고막과 달팽이관 사이 공간'는 \"이관 - 유스타키오관\"을 통해 코 안쪽과 연결되어 있죠. <br></span><span>이 '</span><span>이관'은 수시로 열렸다 <span>닫혔다를 반복하면서 중이의 압력을 조절하고 중이속의 공기를 환기시켜줍니다.&nbsp;터널, 높은 산, 비행기 속에서 귀가 막히는 현상이 있을 때 침을 삼키거나 하품을&nbsp;하면 귀가&nbsp;뚫리는 경험을 해보셨죠? 그게&nbsp;이관이 막히면서 귀가 막히는 느낌이&nbsp;생긴것을&nbsp;이관을 열어주는 행위(하품 등)를 해서&nbsp;중이로&nbsp;공기가 통하게 해주면&nbsp;귀가 뚫리는 느낌이 드는겁니다. <br></span><span>&nbsp;</span></span><br><span><span>그래서 감기, 비염 등 코 문제로 이관이&nbsp;막히게 되면 중이염으로 이어집니다</span></span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" style=\"max-width:234px\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_0_img\", \"src\" : \"http://blogfiles.naver.net/20130610_259/isuhani_1370875754488CxSnD_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B01.PNG\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_0_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9e8a9b2eb3527bb2.png\" width=\"234\" height=\"217\" data-attachment-id=\"\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span>이관이 막히고 중이가 감염되거나 기능적 손상을 일으키는 </span><span>대표적인 원인은 감기, 비염, 등이 있는데 감기가 장기간 지속되면 중이내에 </span><span>세균이 침투해 감염을 일어키고 이관이 부어 급성중이염이 생겨나게 됩니다</span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_1_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0d9efed28aad7032.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_1_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0d9efed28aad7032.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0d9efed28aad7032.jpg\" data-width=\"638\" data-height=\"359\" width=\"638\" height=\"359\" data-attachment-id=\"IH7bLT9t88Cqd7FMmfYD42lupatI\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span></span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span>급성중이염이 시작되면 어린 아이들은 심한 발열과 통증으로 계속해 이유없이 울거나 </span><span>잠을 제대로 이루지 못합니다.</span><br><span>&nbsp;귀는 단지 귀의 문제가 아닌 코와 갚이 관련된 만큼 코 건강에 신경써야 합니다.</span><br><span>특히 <span>콧물 때문에&nbsp;지속적으로&nbsp;강하게 코를 푸는&nbsp;행위는&nbsp;중이염의 원인이 됩니다</span></span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" style=\"max-width:497px\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_2_img\", \"src\" : \"http://blogfiles.naver.net/20130610_101/isuhani_1370875762912gjoSM_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B03.PNG\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_2_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/192b2d71cd69d75b.png\" width=\"497\" height=\"306\" data-attachment-id=\"\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span>문제는 그뿐이 아닙니다. </span><br><span>급성중이염이 발전하여 삼출성중이염이나 만성중이염으로 진행하면 더 골치아픕니다.</span><br><span>​</span><br><span>삼출성중이염은 중이에 물이 고이는&nbsp;겁니다.&nbsp;&nbsp;굽성중이염과 같은 격렬한 </span><br><span>발열과 통증이 없기 때문에 부모들은 오히려 증상이 호전되는 과정으로 착각하기&nbsp; 쉽습니다. 그러나 빨리 호전되지 않고 악화와 완화를 반복하게 되고, 항생제 등 소아과 약을 계속해서 먹게 하는 주된 질병입니다. </span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" style=\"max-width:167px\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_3_img\", \"src\" : \"http://blogfiles.naver.net/20130610_123/isuhani_1370875766959gbyCr_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B04.PNG\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_3_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a3fa11c710acd111.png\" width=\"167\" height=\"218\" data-attachment-id=\"\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span>한방치료는 중이염을 단지 귀에 생긴 염증의 문제로 생각하기 보다 </span><br><span>귀와 관련된 기관들의 기능 손상 및 몸의 면역력저하 문제와 연관지어 </span><br><span>치료의 초점을 맞춥니다.</span><br><span>특히 염증을 발생하게 하는 비염 축농증 등과 같은 </span><span>코 질환들을&nbsp;치료해야 중이염의 뿌리를 뽑을 수&nbsp;있습니다</span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" style=\"max-width:298px\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_4_img\", \"src\" : \"http://blogfiles.naver.net/20130610_118/isuhani_13708757711640U5k6_PNG/%C1%DF%C0%CC%BF%B05.PNG\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_4_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b5f86c7b598db0fe.png\" width=\"298\" height=\"150\" data-attachment-id=\"\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span>&nbsp;</span><br><span>따라서 남성역 이수한의원에서는&nbsp; 아이의 상태를 체계적으로 살피고 </span><span>귀나 코와 관련된 기관의 기능회복과 면역력 강화를 위한 맞춤&nbsp;치료를&nbsp;합니다.</span><br><span><br></span><br><span>한가지 더!</span><br><span>중이염에 오랫동안 시달린 어린이는 성장발육 이 부실한 경우가 많기 때문에 </span><span>정상적인 성장이 잘 이뤄지는지 체크를 하고 문제가 있다면 치료를 함께 하는&nbsp; 것이 좋습니다</span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" style=\"max-width:473px\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_5_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7000bebcd4be3858.png\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_5_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7000bebcd4be3858.png\" width=\"473\" height=\"237\" data-attachment-id=\"\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_6_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d8d1c3e4eea55978.png\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img id=\"SEDOC-1521768895931--1238394153_image_6_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d8d1c3e4eea55978.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazona